 134:Middlewares/ST/threadx/ports/cortex_m33/gnu/inc/tx_port.h **** /* Define the system API mappings based on the error checking
 135:Middlewares/ST/threadx/ports/cortex_m33/gnu/inc/tx_port.h ****    selected by the user.  Note: this section is only applicable to
 136:Middlewares/ST/threadx/ports/cortex_m33/gnu/inc/tx_port.h ****    application source code, hence the conditional that turns off this
 137:Middlewares/ST/threadx/ports/cortex_m33/gnu/inc/tx_port.h ****    stuff when the include file is processed by the ThreadX source. */
 138:Middlewares/ST/threadx/ports/cortex_m33/gnu/inc/tx_port.h **** 
